node.accessibility_caption: Photo by DAILY DOSE on September 02, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Don't look for pretty face, it will turn old one day. Don't look for soft skin, it will wrinkle one day. But look for a loyal heart, that will miss you everyday and love you forever.'.
Photo by DAILY DOSE on September 01, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'I have a sad story too. No one cares. Work harder.'.
Photo by DAILY DOSE on August 31, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'I wanna get married in 2-3 years so I'm going to need one of y'all to act right... Thanks. @DailyDose'.
Photo by DAILY DOSE on August 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'First, know your worth. Second, control your emotions. Third, never settle.'.
Photo by DAILY DOSE on August 28, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Become Unreachable To Those That Had All Access And Abused It.'.
